\SE[7]S-Sorry... I-I put too much effort and... I-I lost my
way...
\SE[8]It would be nice if this cave leads somewhere...

......\.......\........ \!I didn't expect you to come all
the way to this corner. You must be a really exploration-
loving and perverted person....

Well, whatever. \!It would be that if I sent you back empty-
handed, so I'll spare you with a decently strong item.
I won't give you anything anymore! Just go home already...!!
